<p>
	This gorgeous and unique tarot of Fey enables us to discover an enchanted world that cannot help but move and capture the heart. This wonderful deck of tarot was created by Riccardo Minetti and Mara Aghem illustrating landscapes with mysterious and intriguing Fey folk through a powerful use of colour and composition. Whether one believes in their existence or denies it as though dreaming it, the Fey creatures speak through the symbols of the imagination, the infinite potential of the universe. This is the interpretive key: by observing each Fey, we look at ourselves beyond the mirror of appearance. This gorgeous deck of Fey tarot includes 78 cards with complete divining instructions. This magical tarot deck is well-thought out and carefully designed for readers of all ages and a beautiful, playful deck full of its own unique magic.</p>
